is the cold war over mikhail gorbachev and 
ronald reagan say yes george bush suggests no a difference of 
opinion more like a difference of semantics says bush 
humpty dumpty in lewis carrolls through the looking glass 
tells alice when i use a word it means just what i choose it 
to mean neither more nor less 
dumpty would fit right in as a speechwriter at the bush white 
