it would lead to great social tensions and reproaches he added 
on july 2 the nearly worthless east german mark will be 
replaced by highly valuable west german marks the exchange rate 
will be oneforone under communism east german black marketeers 
were willing to pay seven or even 10 to one 
klaus friedrich former head of german affairs at the federal 
reserve predicted that east germany will achieve west german 
living standards in 10 years as a result of unification 
friedrich now with the institute of international finance also 
foresaw east german unemployment skyrocketing from 1 percent to 11 
