a team of five surgeons worked with highpowered microscopes to 
replace the womans entire scalp small blood vessels and other 
tissues torn from her head last week in a vineyard accident in napa 
valley 
she was an attractive woman beforeshe will be an attractive 
woman when its over said dr alfonso oliva who conducted the 
