the rescue of the unisured satellite is expected to cost 
intelsat more than half of the 1465 million price for a 
nongovernment shuttle mission 
nasa has the technological knowhow to reboost the satellite 
and we want to take advantage of nasas expertise so we can boost 
the satellite and it will have a 10year lifespan said company 
