salvation front denied his movement wishes to turn the country 
into a oneparty religious state 
we guarantee the freedom of all who have ideas on algerias 
future he said 
the algerian people are not stupid added madani 59 the 
truth is the best way to answer all questions 
algerias islamic salvation front seeks to establish the islamic 
legal code the sharia as law 
