fronts 12000 candidates for office in tuesdays voting were women 
for months fundamentalist supporters have been accused of 
harassing single women and disrupting nightclubs in algiers 
the fundamentalist party boasts 650000 members many are drawn 
from the ranks of unemployed youth attracted by its fiery mix of 
islam and politics 
