fyffes which has 26 european subsidiaries 
united brands argued that the sale violated its exclusive 
contract with the producers which expires in 1991 with a judges 
consent the company had employees go to the dock where a fyffes 
shipment was waiting and throw tens of thousands of boxes of 
bananas into the sea give them away to local people or stomp on 
them 
