new yorkap final dowjones avgs for wed jun 13 
except for the closing the averages are calculated from the 
open highest and lowest prices for each of the component stocks 
regardless of when each occured for examplethe high for the 30 
industrials is the highest that each reached during the trading 
day not the highest that the 30 reached as a group that means the 
average itself may never have attained the combined high of each of 
its components 
